These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
Pet: turtle, cat, rat, chinchilla, hedgehog
Color: blue, pink, light-blue, azure, chestnut
1. Color:azure is in an odd position##4
2. Color:azure is in the middle##1
3. Pet:hedgehog is on the left or right of Color:blue##3
4. Pet:rat is on the right of Pet:chinchilla##1
5. Pet:turtle is between Color:azure and Color:light-blue##2
6. Pet:hedgehog is in the middle##1
7. Color:azure is on the right of Color:chestnut##1
8. Pet:chinchilla is on the left or right of Pet:hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Pet          | cat | turtle | hedgehog | chinchilla | rat |
| Color   | light-blue  | chestnut      | azure   | blue     | pink    |

