.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
Color: blood-red, aquamarine, fuchsia, lavender, orange
Game: whist, go, scrabble, snooker, backgammon
1. Color:blood-red is in an even position##4
2. Color:blood-red is on the right of Game:snooker##1
3. Color:orange is in the middle##1
4. Game:backgammon is on the left or right of Color:orange##3
5. Game:whist is between Color:fuchsia and Game:snooker##2
6. Game:scrabble is on the right of Color:blood-red##1
7. Color:fuchsia is on the left of Color:lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Color   | fuchsia     | lavender       | orange    | blood-red | aquamarine   |
| Game      | go | whist | snooker | backgammon      | scrabble |

