.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
City: rome, new-york, nizza, hamburg, marseilles
Transport: car, taxi, motorbike, ship, train
1. Transport:ship == City:rome##1
2. Transport:taxi is in an even position##4
3. Transport:taxi is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1
4. City:new-york is on the left or right of Transport:car##3
5. Transport:motorbike is on the left or right of Transport:car##3
6. Transport:train is on the left or right of Transport:taxi##3
7. City:nizza is on the right of City:rome##1
8. City:marseilles is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| City         | rome | nizza | new-york | hamburg    | marseilles |
| Transport   | ship     | car        | motorbike      | taxi | train      |

