2. Color:pink is in an even position##4
3. Color:lavender is on the far right##1
4. Nationality:canadian == Color:lavender##1
5. Nationality:polish is on the right of Color:mauve##1
6. Nationality:american is between Color:coral and Nationality:canadian##2
7. Color:mauve == Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Nationality         | thai      | brazilian | polish | american   | canadian  |
| Color   | grey | mauve    | coral        | pink | lavender |

