4. Movie-Genre:musical is on the right of Sport:ice-hockey##1
5. Sport:soccer == Movie-Genre:musical##1
6. Sport:soccer is in an even position##4
7. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:fantasy##3
8. Sport:baseball is on the right of Movie-Genre:musical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific        | fantasy                | martial-arts  | musical  | action            |
| Sport        | water-polo | climbing | ice-hockey | soccer | baseball |

