1. House:gothic-revival is on the far left or far right##3
2. Beverage:sprite == Beverage:sprite##1
3. Beverage:coffee is on the far left##1
4. Beverage:7up is on the left or right of House:modern##3
5. House:modern is between House:farmhouse and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
6. Beverage:iced-tea is between House:gothic-revival and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
7. Beverage:coffee is in an odd position##4
8. Beverage:hot-chocolate == House:cottage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| House         | gothic-revival | futuristic | cottage | modern | farmhouse     |
| Beverage   | coffee    | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate       | sprite | 7up |

